snippet: Madison Weekly had 20 points, including a season-high five 3-pointers, Hannah Schonhardt had her second double-double of the season and Northern Iowa beat No. 24 Kansas State 67-59 on Thursday night....
lead_paragraph: Madison Weekly had 20 points, including a season-high five 3-pointers, Hannah Schonhardt had her second double-double of the season and Northern Iowa beat No. 24 Kansas State 67-59 on Thursday night.
